column3: “Was told to try this in place of platinum wreck for my knee cap dislocation pain, pain was gone in the first 15 minutes or so and was very very stoned. This was the same knee cap I dislocated twice before and destroyed the MCL last year in it with meniscus tearing, so pretty impressive anti inflammatory and pain relief med and the very strong relaxing sensation that comes with is fantastic great for deep sleep too bu...”
“Works for Restless leg and other joint and back pain. Helps with stress and anxiety. Helps you fall asleep as well. In MY experience, I got aroused easier as well as INCREDABLE sex and orgasms.”

I have Fibro,and it helps with that,GREAT ANTI-Inflamatory...Gives relief for digestive problems,especially nausea...”

column1: Good for nausea and general pain.

column3: “Amazing kick! Terrible flavors. This bud is so dense. One chillum full will stone this 35 year plus smoker of indicas for 4 hours! IMHO it's way too strong to taste so bad. Overly woody/stemmy, bitter, earthy...whatever pc description you can put here that means tastes like...well you're picking up what I'm putting down right?”

Also, it has a weird sushi odor/taste about it... (not a BFD if you're a regular sushi-eater like me)...wh...”

Agree with previous “grape” flavor descriptions. This was delicious. Smooth flavor inhaled and exhaled.

Make any party a good one with Cheese Quake. Thanks CannaFarms!!...”

the smell is very a louring and sweet. the scents of berries, lavender and of the skunky cheese. it smells like a desert. great after dinner smoke. tga's website's discretion is spot on.
